              "content": "=You are a recruitment assistant. Analyze the match between this CV and job posting.\n\nCV:\n{{ $('Extract from PDF').item.json.text }}\n\nJob Posting text (ignore any HTML, JavaScript or navigation menus, focus only on the actual job description):\n{{ $('Normalize Job Text').item.json.job_text }}\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON, no explanation, no markdown, concise written:\n{\n  \"match_score\": \"integer (0-100)\",\n  \"strengths\": [\"string\"],\n  \"critical_gaps\": [\"string\"],\n  \"improvements\": [\"string\"],\n  \"recommendation\": \"enum: Apply | Consider | Skip\"\n}\n\nRules:\n- No explanations\n- No markdown\n- No extra text\n- If missing, use null"
